Thank you so much for sending those through, really appreciate it

Just a quick update to let you know that the Charles, Lennon, McCartney, and Stimson Duo floorplans have all now been successfully added and are displaying correctly on the site.

Feel free to let us know if you spot anything or if you’d like any tweaks made, happy to help

Hi Ash,

Thank you so much for your patience.

Our team has completed the three urgent fixes you flagged, and everything should now be working as expected:
  • Double-story display active, showing both floors on the same page with a magnify option.
  • The “reverse” button on the floor plan image is now functional.
  • Selecting a different house size updates the view without opening a new browser tab.

We also wanted to flag that there are no available flip images for the following FF series:
  • Charles
  • Lennon
  • McCartney
  • Stimson

When you have a moment, could you send the flip images for the following series and we can add it for you

Please let us know if this is okay for you or if you’d like us to take any additional steps.

Hi Ash, Thanks for the call earlier. I've updated the document here and our team is currently completing the urgent fixes you flagged for the website's usability.
  • The double-story display to be active, showing both floors on the same page with a magnify option.
  • Fixing the non-functional "reverse" button on the floor plan image.
  • Selecting a different house size to update the view without opening a new browser tab.
Our support team support@wolfiq.com.au will confirm once completed. Thanks again, Andy
